{"tid":2201315,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒記者今年8.31被捕 活在惡法陰霾下 仍盼以鏡頭記錄保障港人權益：有啲嘢記者先做到","createTime":"2020-09-13T16:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T17:46:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"30094bcf8acf22c217c4d6492948cc633bcfaf69","tid":2201315,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"去年的8.31成港殤之日，但警暴的夢魘持續到今年，更延伸至外媒身上。有在港出生的日媒記者於今年8.31途經旺角時，被警員拉扯背包截查，因身上有懷疑氣槍，以涉嫌仿製槍械被捕。福田（Fukuda Nozomi）接受《蘋果》訪問時大嘆無奈，即使氣槍合乎規格仍然被警方沒收，「警方會唔會對支槍做啲咩？我完全唔知道」。為免讓自己身負多罪，他坦言採訪工作受到心理上的窒礙，尤以《國安法》下，警方針對外媒之舉日益嚴重，「可能會企遠啲影，帶望遠鏡」。不過，這位行家希望繼續以鏡頭記錄香港示威，以照片保障被捕人的權益，「有啲嘢係記者先做得到」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/II6GN3TN4RGBTJ3MNLHENASOB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FII6GN3TN4RGBTJ3MNLHENASOB4%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8N7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=32b6518b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FII6GN3TN4RGBTJ3MNLHENASOB4%2F&h=ec2c197c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/II6GN3TN4RGBTJ3MNLHENASOB4/</a>"},{"pid":"52668c4a40a0d7f85a8a0b121cd0a32e4a2297a7","tid":2201315,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffc51779af494b916df29b989d167a837b137ac","tid":2201315,"uid":184597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69a3c6b01c4b449fbbb2a673c51f99ce24973d5","tid":2201315,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"